ED_Title: Proposed programme of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) for the seventy-fourth session of the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 48th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2018, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee),  approved the proposed programme of work and timetable of the Fourth Committee for the seventy-fourth session of the Assembly, as set out in the report of the Committee.
